settings.description: Fed up with Mario beating them up time and time again, all of the enemies turn giganto! Use the starman to blast your way through these larger-than-life foes.
Roto-discs are like Fire Bars, but with much more room to dodge! Just make sure to keep your wits about you; they're a lot faster, too!
A volarr con la capa de mario XD
Mario takes two floating platforms on a joyride!
Mario tiene que conseguir el cofre antes que sea demasiado tarde
REISSUE: Mario's least threatening foes have come together to create insanity in the sewers. Prod. Code: 105, Rel: 5/25/22 -- 8:56 am. I had no new levels finished, so I'm just pushing this out.
Hammers are practically everywhere, attacking from all sides! Make sure to avoid them!

Guide your way through this tough world with your skills and expertise! This world will train your ability to.. do stuff?
--Use with Mario, Luigi is pretty hard to complete--
